# Solicitation Review Report: W912P525RA008 – Old Hickory Lake Operation & Maintenance Services

---

## 1. SUMMARY & FIT TO QUALIFICATIONS

**Solicitation Title:** Old Hickory Lake Operation and Maintenance Services Requirements Contract, 2026–2030

**Scope:**
- Contractor to provide management, personnel, materials, supplies, tools, parts, equipment, and vehicles for mowing, cleaning, janitorial, and other maintenance services at recreation/project areas around Old Hickory Lake, TN.
- Work includes ongoing maintenance, facility support, janitorial services — all non-clinical/medical.

**Location:** Hendersonville, Tennessee (Old Hickory Lake Project)

**Contract Type:** Firm-Fixed Price, Requirements Contract (Indefinite Delivery)
- **Duration:** Base Year + Four Option Years
- **Set Aside:** Small Business
- **NAICS:** 561210 (Facilities Support Services), $47M size standard

**Insurance:**
- Standard requirements likely include: worker's compensation, general liability, automotive liability. Full details in Performance Work Statement (PWS).

**Evaluation:** Best Value, with technical merit, past performance, and price. Not lowest-cost-only.

**Proposal Deadline:** Nov 12, 2025, 13:00 CT (Amended from Nov 6)
**Site Visit:** Oct 15, 2025, 10:00 am CT at Old Hickory Lake Resource Office

**Contact:**
- Samantha Clay
- Samantha.J.Clay@usace.army.mil, 615-330-0089

